fmain.c:

-DCMAIN=name is not standard.
HAVE_IARGC should be determined by configure

How to decide on syscall CCOMP switches should be done by configure.
Three functions:

      subroutine getarf(iarg,strn)
possibilities:
C#ifdef HASNARGC
C#elseifC HASIARGC
C#elseifC HASNARGS
C#endif

      integer function nargf()
possibilities:
C#ifdef HASNARGC
C#elseifC HASIARGC
C#elseifC HASNARGS

      subroutine ftime(datim)
possibilities
C#ifdef FCTIME
C#elseifC FDATE
